msgid ""
"Calculate the Conditional Value at Risk (CVaR) at a specified confidence "
"level."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el Valor en Riesgo Condicional (CVaR) a un nivel de confianza "
"especificado."

#: 8b8f74e6e2c84798babeb0abb21e6290 of
#: pymc_marketing.mmm.utility.conditional_value_at_risk:4
msgid ""
"CVaR, also known as Expected Shortfall, measures the average loss exceeding "
"the VaR at a given confidence level, providing insight into the tail risk of"
" the distribution."
msgstr ""
"CVaR, también conocido como Pérdida Esperada, mide la pérdida promedio que "
"excede el VaR a un nivel de confianza dado, proporcionando información sobre"
" el riesgo de cola de la distribución."

#: 7ebf19f8c9a74236adaf633578dcbb18 of
#: pymc_marketing.mmm.utility.conditional_value_at_risk:7
msgid "The Conditional Value at Risk (CVaR) is calculated as:"
msgstr "El Valor en Riesgo Condicional (CVaR) se calcula como:"

#: d0351e0c722c473da9ee93c3f6c31f1a of
#: pymc_marketing.mmm.utility.conditional_value_at_risk:9
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"CVaR = \\mathbb{E}[X \\mid X \\leq VaR]\n"
"\n"
msgstr "CVaR = \\mathbb{E}[X \\mid X \\leq VaR]"

#: 21a63438f21e4c5b9deb513f696292de of
#: pymc_marketing.mmm.utility.conditional_value_at_risk:12
msgid ""
"where :math:`X` represents the loss distribution, and :math:`VaR` is the "
"Value at Risk at the specified confidence level. CVaR provides a more "
"comprehensive view of the risk associated with extreme losses beyond the "
"VaR."
msgstr ""
"donde :math:`X` representa la distribución de pérdidas, y :math:`VaR` es el "
"Valor en Riesgo en el nivel de confianza especificado. CVaR proporciona una "
"visión más completa del riesgo asociado con pérdidas extremas más allá del "
"VaR."

